== 定义 ==
{{see also|最大风速半径}}
最大持续风速通常出现在热带气旋内距风暴中心还有一段距离的位置，这段距离被称为[[最大风速半径|最大风速半径]]，并且通常都在风眼墙中，距离进一步拉大后，风速又会开始减慢<ref>{{cite web|author1=Brian W. Blanchard |author2=S. A. Hsu |url=http://www.nwas.org/ej/pdf/2006-EJ4.pdf |title=ON THE RADIAL VARIATION OF THE TANGENTIAL WIND SPEED OUTSIDE THE RADIUS OF MAXIMUM WIND DURING HURRICANE WILMA (2005) |publisher=Louisiana State University |work=Coastal Studies Institute |accessdate=2014-02-23 |location=Baton Rouge, Louisiana |archivedate=2012-09-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905133143/http://www.nwas.org/ej/pdf/2006-EJ4.pdf |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。大部分气象部门都会使用[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]推荐的持续风速定义，即在距地表十米高的位置测量十分钟并取平均值。不过，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]的测量方式有所不同，其测量高度仍然是十米，但测量的时间范围则缩短到了一分钟<ref name="NWSM Defs">{{cite web | author = Tropical Cyclone Weather Services Program | title = Tropical cyclone definitions | url = http://www.weather.gov/directives/sym/pd01006004curr.pdf | format = PDF | date = 2006-06-01 | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | publisher = National Weather Service | archivedate = 2013-11-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111165801/http://www.nws.noaa.gov/directives/sym/pd01006004curr.pdf}}</ref>。这是一个非常重要的区别，因为一分钟持续风速的数值要比十分钟持续风速的数值大14%<ref>{{cite web | publisher = United States Navy | url = http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/pubs/TC_Forecasters_Guide/chap6/se200.htm | title = SECTION 2. INTENSITY OBSERVATION AND FORECAST ERRORS | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | archive-date = 2021-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211216043955/https://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/pubs/TC_Forecasters_Guide/chap6/se200.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 数值测定 ==
大部分地区都会把[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]作为确定热带气旋最大持续风速的主要方法，这种方法是以[[气象卫星|气象卫星]]的观测数值来进行判断<ref name="ODT">{{cite web | author1 = Christopher S. Velden |author2 = Timothy L. Olander | author3 = Raymond M. Zehr | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223085207/http://tropic.ssec.wisc.edu/misc/adt/odt/odt.html | title= Objective Dvorak Technique | url = http://tropic.ssec.wisc.edu/misc/adt/odt/odt.html | publisher = University of Wisconsin–Madison | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | archivedate = 2014-02-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，通过对螺旋[[雨带|带]]的规模和风眼与风眼墙之间的温度差来确定热带气旋的最大持续风速和[[气压|气压]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Chris Landsea | date = 2010-06-08 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/H1.html | title = Subject: H1) What is the Dvorak technique and how is it used? | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | archivedate = 2014-01-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140125190925/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/H1.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[低气压|低气压区]]中心的[[气压|中心气压]]值为估计值。飓风的强度则是根据[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]时间和最大强度一起得出<ref name="NHC SSHS">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | title = Saffir-Simpson Hurricane Scale Information | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2006-06-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140111191521/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutsshws.php | archivedate = 2014-01-11 |url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutsshws.php | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。对精细卫星图像上单独云层的追踪还可以用来进一步估计热带气旋的表面风速<ref>{{cite web | author1 = A. F. Hasler | author2 = K. Palaniappan | author3 = C. Kambhammetu | author4 = P. Black | author5 = E. Uhlhorn | author6 = D. Chesters | url = http://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/abs/10.1175/1520-0477(1998)079%3C2483%3AHRWFWT%3E2.0.CO%3B2 | title = High-Resolution Wind Fields within the Inner Core and Eye of a Mature Tropical Cyclone from GOES 1-min Images | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | archive-date = 2020-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200609004726/https://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/abs/10.1175/1520-0477(1998)079%3C2483%3AHRWFWT%3E2.0.CO%3B2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

如果可以的话，科研人员也会使用船舶和陆地的观测数据。[[大西洋|大西洋]]以及[[太平洋|太平洋]]的中部和东部仍然会动用侦察机飞入热带气旋来确定飞行高度层的风力，这个数据加以调整后可以对最大持续风速做出相当可靠的估算。经过之前十年使用[[全球定位系统|全球定位系统]][[投落送|投落送]]后得出的大量数值已经证实，将飞行高度层取样的风速减少10%以后，就可以用来对接近地表的最大持续风速作出估算<ref name="Franklin">{{cite journal | author1 = James L. Franklin | author2 = Michael L. Black | author3 = Krystal Valde | url = http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=15034652 | title = GPS dropwindsonde wind profiles in hurricanes and their operational implications | issn = 0882-8156 | accessdate = 2014-02-23 |page = 32-44 |year = 2003 |volume=18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120921172526/http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=15034652 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-09-21 | journal = Weather and forecasting}}</ref>。[[气象雷达|多普勒气象雷达]]也可以用来以相同的方法确定接近陆地热带气旋的表面风速<ref>{{cite journal | author1 = J. TUTTLE | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120921172543/http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=1801644 | author2 = R. GALL | url = http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=1801644 | title = A single-radar technique for estimating the winds in tropical cyclones | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | volume = 80 | year = 1999 | journal = Bulletin of the American Meteorological Society | issn = 0003-0007 | archivedate = 2012-09-21 | deadurl = no | pages = 653-668}}</ref>。
