== 变动 ==
{{See also|大气边界层}}
大气与地球表面的磨擦导致地表风速会降低二十个百分点<ref>{{cite web | author = Jeff Haby | archivedate = 2012-06-29 | url = http://www.theweatherprediction.com/habyhints/10/ | title = The Importance of Friction | work = theweatherprediction.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120629074352/http://www.theweatherprediction.com/habyhints/10/ |deadurl=no | accessdate = 2014-02-23}}</ref>，地表的粗糙程度也会对风速产生很大影响。陆地上风速最高的通常是山峰或山脉的峰顶，而山峰和峰顶的阻挡又反过来使得山谷和山坡背的风速更慢<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021080031/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/jht/05-07reports/JHT07_Miller_midyear.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/jht/05-07reports/JHT07_Miller_midyear.pdf | title = Mapping of Topographic Effects on Maximum Sustained Surface Wind Speeds in Landfalling Hurricanes | accessdate = 2014-02-23}}</ref>。与水上相比，陆地上热带风旋的最大持续风速平均要低八个百分点<ref>{{cite web|first=James L. |last=Franklin |date=2002-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003074034/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/august01/Franklin_response%282%29.txt |url=http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/august01/Franklin_response(2).txt |title=Subject: Re: Offshore vs nearshore sonde composite |accessdate=2014-02-23 |archivedate=2013-10-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。更具体地来说，城市或粗糙地形上空的风速与高层[[地转风|地转风]]风速的差距幅度可以达到40%到50%，而在水面或冰面上，差距幅度则是在10%到30%之间<ref name="Franklin" /><ref>{{cite book | last = Harrison | first = Roy | title = Understanding Our Environment | url = https://archive.org/details/understandingour00harr_090 | publisher = Royal Society of Chemistry | location = Cambridge | year = 1999 | isbn = 0-85404-584-8 | page = [https://archive.org/details/understandingour00harr_090/page/n25 11]}}</ref><ref name=Russell>{{cite book | last = Thompson | first = Russell | title = Atmospheric Processes and Systems | publisher = Routledge | location = New York | year = 1998 | isbn = 0-415-17145-8 | pages = 102-103 | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books/about/Atmospheric_Processes_and_Systems.html?id=jSsu8eVx298C | archive-date = 2014-02-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140227151133/http://books.google.com.hk/books/about/Atmospheric_Processes_and_Systems.html?id=jSsu8eVx298C | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 与热带气旋强度分级间的关系 ==
大部分地区都是用最大持续风速来确定热带气旋的强度。例如大西洋和东风太平洋就是使用[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]，该等级可以用来对陆地上因热带气旋而导致的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]和破坏做出估算<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130925065610/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | author = Williams, Jack | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = USA Today | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | url= http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-25}}</ref>。大部分地区的热带气旋强度分级（如热带低气压、热带风暴、飓风、台风、超强台风、低气压、深层低气压、强烈热带气旋）都是根据[[气旋|气旋]]的最大持续风速确定，只有[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]例外，该国海域不会使用最大持续风速来确定热带气旋的强度级别，而是使用阵风风速<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Bureau of Meteorology | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/catalogue/warnings/WarningsInformation_TC_Ed.shtml#Cat | title = Bureau of Meteorology: Tropical Cyclone Information Resources | accessdate = 2007-09-27 | archivedate = 2007-09-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927233700/http://www.bom.gov.au/catalogue/warnings/WarningsInformation_TC_Ed.shtml}}</ref>。

